SIF TALENT:해방
	CFLAG:269 += 3
SIF TALENT:부끄럼쟁이
	CFLAG:269 += 3
SIF TALENT:미련함
	CFLAG:269 += 3
SIF TALENT:음란
	CFLAG:269 += 5
SIF TALENT:연모
	CFLAG:269 += 10
SIF TALENT:망신
	CFLAG:269 += 5
SIF TALENT:서약
